(895, 126, 'challenge', 'Collect, process and visualise the data gathered from power meters, cadence meters, portable lab lactate gauges in order to prepare efficient training plans.'),
(896, 126, '_challenge', 'field_5d63fbea41355'),
(897, 126, 'features', 'Implement many tools for analysing performance and training outcomes.\r\nSending and analyzing measuring device data.\r\nProcessing and graph visualization of the gadget data.\r\nStorage and analysis of training outcomes.\r\nDistant online communication tool for coaching.'),
(898, 126, '_features', 'field_5d63fc0641356'),
(899, 126, 'competitive_adv', 'In the cycling sport the coach cannot permanently be next to the athlete during a race competition or training. Nevertheless, being distanced from the athlete, the coach receives information about the athlete`s health condition and can correct riding.'),
