(2214, 506, 'goal', 'Improve training process based on the objective athletes’ indicators, define sport potential in child.'),
(2215, 506, '_goal', 'field_5d63fbce41353'),
(2216, 506, 'solution', 'We have created the technology that stores athlete`s data entered by athlete or coach manually or automatically with the help of additional devices (such as racquet handle shot analyzers). All data are stored in the athlete’s passport in the system. Based on these data and indicators coach can make decisions about what training plan shall be undertaken to achieve better results. Solution also provides the possibility to create custom training program. It is possible to view training progress in diagrams and graphs.\r\n\r\nTechnology allows identifying sport talent and future perspectives in child to do sport. This talent identification is based on indicator of child’s assessment coordination. This indicator defines the ability of a child to do any sport, or maybe it is more reasonable to move in arts.\r\n\r\nThis technology can be used not only in tennis but in any other sport.'),
(2217, 506, '_solution', 'field_5d63fbde41354'),
(2218, 506, 'challenge', 'Providing objective data.\r\nOptimizing training process.\r\nTracking training results.\r\nCalculating assessment coordination indicator online.'),
(2219, 506, '_challenge', 'field_5d63fbea41355'),
(2220, 506, 'features', 'Creating customizable training plan and exercises.\r\nInputting the training outcomes and indicators.\r\nImplementing sports devices and equipment.\r\nVisualizing all training results.\r\nProviding recommendations for future training plan.'),
(2221, 506, '_features', 'field_5d63fc0641356'),
(2222, 506, 'competitive_adv', 'Gathering and processing great data amount.\r\nRecognizing future sport talents.'),
