(2371, 525, 'solution', 'An athlete interested in improving his/her personal results sends a request to the website. Then the athlete has to answer the questions and enter the most recent swimming results online. The system generates the report containing indications on the athlete’s weaknesses and strengths, and recommendations for the training process to be corrected so that to improve swimming skills.\r\n\r\nOur solution has ensured development of technical content of the app (e.g. by providing access to the website system via mobile phone) and increased its sales.'),
(2372, 525, '_solution', 'field_5d63fbde41354'),
(2373, 525, 'challenge', 'Increase data accuracy and its actualisation from once a week towards real-time.\r\nMove athlete’s training station from PC to a mobile – right to the swimming pool.\r\nMake system scalable towards the growing number of users.\r\nMake training experience social.'),
(2374, 525, '_challenge', 'field_5d63fbea41355'),
(2375, 525, 'features', 'A mobile version as a major training station: training data input, results, training plans etc. are entered within the app.\r\nMultimodal swimming data input (the athlete inputs a set of parameters right after a swim-in).'),
(2376, 525, '_features', 'field_5d63fc0641356'),
(2377, 525, 'competitive_adv', 'Live automated swimming data analysis and visualization.\r\nLive automated feedback for result improvement.\r\nDesktop web portal for coach’s training plan management.'),
