(3273, 638, 'solution', 'LeggUP makes it possible for people from all professional backgrounds to get access to quality coaches. For coaching professionals the system provides a network of eager learners and tech solutions that make it easier to run their business.\r\nLeggUp provides communication facility to fix assignments and appointments, manages bookings and meetings, technically supports trainings (video, messaging and interactive whiteboards), and allows various payment options and transaction and report management.\r\nOur team has been engaged in working out of the project backlog (project specifications), development of system architecture, prototypes, UI, database, frontend and backend, and integration of third party services (payment system, messenger, conference communication). We also provided QA & support, DevOps and compliance with GDPR.'),
