(264, 1, '2019-08-27 10:00:57', '2019-08-27 10:00:57', 'Here the key aim is to figure out the leading users’ Pains, Needs and Desires that drive the product and validate the idea. We are helping to set up the proper process of the unclarities elimination by market/competitor research and analysis, defining the scope, creating Product Backlog and prototyping. After that stage, the pre-product prototype should be confirmed with the end-users in order to move to the next stage or handle the pivot.', 'Ideation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'surging-growth', '', '', '2019-09-30 14:57:35', '2019-09-30 11:57:35', '', 0, 'http://wp-stone-lab/?post_type=startup&#038;p=264', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(265, 1, '2019-08-27 10:01:17', '2019-08-27 10:01:17', 'So, the product demand is verified and the scope is clear, so we are ready to go. Yet having the limited budget from Angel Investors we need to start our journey to success with the Minimum Viable Product. That means that we need very carefully segregate the Backlog in order to implement only top required features which can grant the users traction.', 'Angel Round', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lorem-ipsum-dolor-sit-amet', '', '', '2019-09-30 14:58:59', '2019-09-30 11:58:59', '', 0, 'http://wp-stone-lab/?post_type=startup&#038;p=265', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(266, 1, '2019-08-27 10:01:34', '2019-08-27 10:01:34', 'Now serious game has started – we’ve already crossed the chasm and now the major aim is growth. In order to sustain it lots of technical and organizational improvements should be handled – business processes automation, product scalability and reliability improvements and even tech architecture renovation. Our team is ready to face these challenges and transform the startup into a significant product company.', 'Series A', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lorem-ipsum-dolor-sit-amet-3', '', '', '2019-09-30 15:00:30', '2019-09-30 12:00:30', '', 0, 'http://wp-stone-lab/?post_type=startup&#038;p=266', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
(267, 1, '2019-08-27 10:01:51', '2019-08-27 10:01:51', 'Finally, the solution has become well-established at the market, yet it’s not the end – still there are challenges in order to be competitive, effective and innovative. These aims can be achieved by constant product improvement – decreasing the costs by the dedicated remote development office, new features development and even pivots (startups inside of the startup).', 'Surging Growth', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lorem-ipsum-dolor-sit-amet-4', '', '', '2019-09-30 15:01:37', '2019-09-30 12:01:37', '', 0, 'http://wp-stone-lab/?post_type=startup&#038;p=267', 0, 'startup', '', 0),
